Sorting data

# Arrange by the Treatment, then Time
dat.1 %>% 
  arrange(Treatment, Time)
# Arrange by Treatment, then by the mean of Resp 1 and Resp2
dat.1 %>% 
  mutate(Resp = mean(c(Resp1, Resp2))) %>%
  arrange(Treatment, Resp) %>% 
  head()
